			<CASNumber>1327-41-9</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Polyaluminium Chloride is a water chemical made up of the elements aluminium, oxygen, hydrogen, and chlorine. It is a yellow colored, water soluble solid. It is slightly acidic and acts as a coagulating agent during water treatment process. It is a safer alternative to several other chemical coagulants. It is used in the purification of table water, industry water, industry circulation water and wasted and polluted water from various industries.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">聚合氯化铝是一种由铝、氧、氢和氯元素组成的水化学品。它是一种黄色的水溶性固体。它呈弱酸性，在水处理过程中起凝结剂的作用。与其他几种化学混凝剂相比，它是一种更安全的替代品。它可用于净化食水、工业用水、工业循环水以及各行各业的废水和污染水。</common:generalComment>
